com.genband.kandy.api.services.calls.statistics

Interface IKandyCallGeneralAudioRTPStatistics

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IKandyCallStatistic
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    KandyCallGeneralAudioRTPStatistics

    public interface IKandyCallGeneralAudioRTPStatistics
extends IKandyCallStatistic
    Defines general statistics of an audio call. (We have 3 types of audio/video call statistics : "receive" (which data is received); "sent" (which data was sent) and "general")
